short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Set proxy for Google Chrome browser

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Simple proxy helper is an extension that allows people to connect to webRTC providers through a SOCKS5 proxy in case they cannot access it directly due to communication or infrastructure problems. The proxy only works for a limited set of webRTC providers. The extension is for internal use.
